  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0db6\u0dba\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "President's resignation letter to the audience",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliamentary Secretary General Dhammika Dasanayake presented the President's resignation letter to Parliament today.",
        "It is mentioned in the article that due to the need to shut down the country from time to time in the years 2020-2021 to protect the people from the Corona epidemic situation, the government had to face the further development of the economic crisis that had been growing for many years and a shortage of foreign exchange.",
        "In order to find a solution to the resulting instability, it is stated in the letter of resignation that she made every effort to form an all-party or national government by inviting all political party leaders representing the parliament.",
        "Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapakse states in his resignation letter that he will resign from the presidency effective July 14 as per the request of the common people and the parliamentary party leaders and that he will continue to contribute to the motherland in the same way as he has served with maximum energy till now."
      ],
